p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2016-09-24 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(28,'Hiking @ Evan\'s peak trail','hiking','<p>继续上次未曾完成的线路</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.ca/maps/dir/49.3272286,-122.4630031/49.3388996,-122.4773766/@49.3307188,-122.4787605,15z/data=!4m2!4m1!3e2?hl=en\">https://www.google.ca/maps/dir/49.3272286,-122.4630031/49.3388996,-122.4773766/@49.3307188,-122.4787605,15z/data=!4m2!4m1!3e2?hl=en</a></p>\r\n','2016-05-21 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(29,'Manning Park 看山花','camping','<p>去年没看到花开，希望今年能如愿</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D1. checkin &nbsp;(hiking @ heather trail)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D2. checkout &nbsp;lake tour</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://www.env.gov.bc.ca/bcparks/explore/parkpgs/ecmanning/heather.html\">Heather Trail&nbsp;</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Distance: 19 km (return)<br />\r\nTime: 7.5 hours<br />\r\nLow point: 1793 m<br />\r\nHigh point: 2272 m<br />\r\nElevation gain: 479 m<br />\r\nCumulative Elevation gain: 930 m<br />\r\nCalories burned: 5000</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trailhead: 49&deg; 6&rsquo; 12&rdquo; by &nbsp;120&deg; 45&rsquo; 32&rdquo; (<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/6VhjT\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Trailhead\">Google Map</a>)<br />\r\nLocation to turn off Hwy 3: 49&deg; 3&rsquo; 47&rdquo; by &nbsp;120&deg; 46&rsquo; 57.5&rdquo; (<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/AQrV8\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Trailhead\">Google Map</a>)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"IMG_7963\" src=\"http://www.buntzenlake.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/IMG_7963.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"IMG_8021\" src=\"http://www.buntzenlake.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/IMG_8021.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"IMG_8103\" src=\"http://www.buntzenlake.ca/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/IMG_8103.jpg\" /></p>\r\n','2016-08-06 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(30,'Camping @ Sasquatch','camping','<p>去年去hiking 发现不错的地方camping</p>\r\n\r\n<p>旁边的deer lake 可以顺道去看看</p>\r\n\r\n<p>营地看运气了,先到先得,需要早点去</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D1: &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Checkin campsite : Deer lake or Hicks lake</li>\r\n	<li>hiking @ deer lake</li>\r\n	<li>fire talk</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>D2:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Breakfast</li>\r\n	<li>Checkout</li>\r\n	<li>Harrison water park</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2016-07-16 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(31,'Hiking @ Norvan Falls','hiking','<p><a href=\"https://www.vancouvertrails.com/trails/norvan-falls/\">https://www.vancouvertrails.com/trails/norvan-falls/</a></p>\r\n','2016-07-01 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(32,'Hiking to Bowen Lookout','hiking sypress','<p>warm up for HSCT</p>\r\n\r\n<p>single trip 2.3km</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.ca/maps/dir/Cypress+Mountain/Bowen+Lookout/@49.4027125,-123.2162764,15z/data=!4m14!4m13!1m5!1m1!1s0x0:0x821712a6c6d32ff3!2m2!1d-123.204545!2d49.396018!1m5!1m1!1s0x0:0xe6f583c4bda9b5d4!2m2!1d-123.2137889!2d49.4065105!3e2?hl=en\">https://www.google.ca/maps/dir/Cypress+Mountain/Bowen+Lookout/@49.4027125,-123.2162764,15z/data=!4m14!4m13!1m5!1m1!1s0x0:0x821712a6c6d32ff3!2m2!1d-123.204545!2d49.396018!1m5!1m1!1s0x0:0xe6f583c4bda9b5d4!2m2!1d-123.2137889!2d49.4065105!3e2?hl=en</a></p>\r\n','2016-07-30 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(33,'Go sailing @ English Bay','sailing','<p>12:00pm</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>John</li>\r\n	<li>Carl</li>\r\n	<li>Richard</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','2016-07-10 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(34,'Camping @ Chilliwack Lake','camping','<p>不是在hiking</p>\r\n\r\n<p>就是在camping</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D1. checkin campsite and relax</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D2: hiking to Lindeman Lake</p>\r\n\r\n<p>D3: checkout&nbsp;</p>\r\n','2016-07-30 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(35,'BBQ party @ Belcarra ','bbq','<p>A baby &nbsp;- 100 days!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Location : Belcarra Picnic Area</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Checklist:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Stove</li>\r\n	<li>Boat</li>\r\n	<li>Crab trap</li>\r\n	<li>餐巾纸</li>\r\n	<li>纸盘</li>\r\n	<li>刀叉</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Food list: BBQ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Richard - 鸡翅,花生,毛豆,蘑菇</li>\r\n	<li>水果：西瓜，蓝莓，苹果，葡萄</li>\r\n	<li>Jack Qi - 虾，意大利香肠，牛肉，蛋糕，西瓜</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','2016-07-24 03:00:00',1,'zh-cn'),(36,'Hiking @ Lynn Peak','hiking','<p><a href=\"https:/